beer.beer_description: Social media is a special place. We always like to take note of the most enjoyable comments we see out there, and one of our favorites had to do with a particular hop blend, specifically stating that “Don't Know About That….Hop" Whereas in this instance it didn’t appear in the dry hop, but only in the whirlpool in such a minuscule amount that the chances of getting any flavors from it were nonexistent. So welcome to our series where we explore seeing what hops can do solo! All Hail the mighty Amarillo!
